Class GasStation.Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.model.GasStation.Product
  • Enclosing class:
    GasStation

    public class GasStation.Product
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a product available in a gas station.

    Typically, this product is a type of fuel.
